            <para>The DVD structure is not present. This may be caused by incompatible drive/medium used.</para>
            <para>Value: 0xC0AA020E</para>
          </description>
        </item>
        <item>
          <description>
            <para>
              <b>E_IMAPI_RECORDER_NO_SUCH_MODE_PAGE</b>
